       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. T6KYC01.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-UPDATE.
           05  WS-UPDATE-RECEIVED    PIC X VALUE 'N'.
           05  WS-QUEUE-STATUS       PIC X(8) VALUE SPACES.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       1000-MAIN.
           ACCEPT WS-UPDATE-RECEIVED
           PERFORM 2000-QUEUE-CKYCR
           DISPLAY WS-QUEUE-STATUS
           STOP RUN.
       2000-QUEUE-CKYCR.
           IF WS-UPDATE-RECEIVED = 'Y'
              MOVE 'PENDING' TO WS-QUEUE-STATUS
           ELSE
              MOVE 'NOUPDATE' TO WS-QUEUE-STATUS
           END-IF.
